GUI is built with Qt/PySide and Qt Creator for UI design.

UNIX:
=====

Debian-based:

# apt-get install python-pyside pyside-tools qtcreator

Convert UI to Python code:

% pyside-uic TimeroomMainWindow.ui -o TimeroomMainWindow.py

Windows:
========

Install Python, PySide and cfx_freeze (all available as binaries)

Generate a standalone executable:

Building Windows executables:

> C:\Python2.7\Scripts\cfxfreeze timeroomgui.py --target-dir dist --base-name Win32GUI --include-modules atexit
